Ah, too bad, you got caught in a web! Well, you can continue on through the maze, to complete it, of course, not to spend some more time all wrapped up, or you can exit immediately, in case any clumsy adventurers find their way in here, and \fidont\fi want to be fucked a dozen times before they get out. Your call.
\fi\c[25]As soon as you press Z, you will have one second to move off the web you are standing on before they reactivate.

\fiHello, and welcome, to Spider Alley! Navigate the tight maze of spiderwebs, using the launch pads to your advantagewhile avoiding the ones positioned to send you to your perilas you make your way to the exit on the far right! Or get wrapped up in some sticky webs, and enjoy some quality time with our Arachnes! These webs are a bit more potent than the ones you might have encountered earlier in our little dungeon, so there wont be any fighting your way out of the sticky situation you end up in. And if you arent picked up by any Arachnes, worry not, Im sure some cute adventurer while come by and rescue you.
Congrats on making it to the exit! I hope you weren't expecting a reward, because I haven't prepared one! Bye now.
